    "en": {
      "title": "To date, 46 people have been deported",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "46 Sri Lankans who tried to enter Australia illegally were arrested by the Australian authorities and deported this morning (30).",
        "The deportees were from the Chilaw area and included two children under the age of five.",
        "All of them will be produced before the Negombo Magistrate's Court, airport sources said."
      ],
